'''夏巴大道'''（{{lang-fa|چهارباغ}}，Chahar Bagh，意为“四个花园”）是[[伊朗|伊朗]][[伊斯法罕|伊斯法罕]]一条历史悠久的街道，建于[[萨菲王朝|萨菲王朝]]。

夏巴大道南北走向，5.5公里长，连接城市的北部和南部。在这条街的东侧，有八天堂宫（Hasht Behesht）和[[四十柱宫|四十柱宫]]花园<ref>Lehrman, Jonas Benzion (1980). ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=WwH5L6u6tu0C Earthly paradise: garden and courtyard in Islam] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=WwH5L6u6tu0C |date=20160629163937 }}''. University of California Press. ISBN 0520043634. pp. 116-126.</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Assari|first=Ali|author2=T.M. Mahesh|title=Conservation of historic urban core in traditional Islamic culture: case study of Isfahan city|journal=Indian Journal of Science and Technology|date=January 2012|volume=5|issue=1|pages=1970–1976|url=http://www.indjst.org/archive/jan-12-web/34-jan12aliassari.pdf|accessdate=7 January 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027112204/http://www.indjst.org/archive/jan-12-web/34-jan12aliassari.pdf|archivedate=2012年10月27日}}</ref>。

==历史==
阿巴斯一世从[[加兹温|加兹温]]迁都到[[伊斯法罕|伊斯法罕]]，决定倾全国之力营建新都。首席建筑师是Shaykh Bahai<ref>Kheirabadi Masoud (2000). ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=HEumaflGM_cC Iranian Cities: Formation and Development] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HEumaflGM_cC |date=20160624042934 }}''. Syracuse University Press. pp. 47.</ref> 负责阿巴斯规划中的两个关键项目：夏巴大道，和[[伊玛目广场|伊玛目广场]]<ref>Sir Roger Stevens; ''The Land of the Great Sophy'', p. 172.</ref><ref name="Ali Assari">{{cite journal|last=Assari|first=Ali|author2=Erfan Assari|title=Urban spirit and heritage conservation problems: case study Isfahan city in Iran|journal=Journal of American Science|year=2012|volume=8|issue=1|pages=203–209|url=http://www.jofamericanscience.org/journals/am-sci/am0801/030_7701am0801_203_209.pdf|accessdate=7 January 2013|archive-date=2012-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022052348/http://www.jofamericanscience.org/journals/am-sci/am0801/030_7701am0801_203_209.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==分段==
夏巴大道分为三段：北段的下夏巴（Chaharbagh Pa'in，{{lang-fa|چهارباغ پایین}})，从Shohada 广场到 Darvazeh Dowlat；中段的中夏巴（Chaharbagh Abbasi, ({{lang-fa|چهارباغ عباسی}})，从 Darvazeh Dowlat 到[[三十三孔桥|三十三孔桥]]；南段的上夏巴（Chaharbagh Bala, ,({{lang-fa|چهارباغ بالا}}).从[[三十三孔桥|三十三孔桥]]到Azadi 广场。 

